		"description" : "<p><img alt=%34%34 src=%34%2fsites%2fdefault%2ffiles%2f10359_005_logo.jpg%34 style=%34padding-top%3a 0px; padding-right%3a 0px; padding-bottom%3a 20px; padding-left%3a 20px; float%3a right; width%3a 155px; height%3a 55px; %34 %2f>Next week <a href=%34http%3a%2f%2fwww.janrain.com%34>Janrain<%2fa> will be speaking at <a href=%34http%3a%2f%2fwww.wbresearch.com%2fetailusaeast%2fhome.aspx%34 target=%34_blank%34>eTail East<%2fa> in Baltimore, MD, one of the largest annual internet retail conferences.<%2fp>				
											<p>Janrain CEO, Brian Kissel, will be on a panel on Wednesday, August 11 on the important topic of %38ldquo;<strong>Re-designing Your Website to Increase Conversion Rates %38amp; Better Engage Customers.<%2fstrong>%38quot; Bill Aicher, Director of Web and Marketing of <a href=%34http%3a%2f%2fMusicnotes.com%34 target=%34_blank%34>Musicnotes.com<%2fa> and Josh Himwich, Director of eCommerce Solutions of <a href=%34http%3a%2f%2fDiapers.com%34 target=%34_blank%34>Diapers.com<%2fa> will join Kissel in this discussion about identifying your strategic goals when redesigning your website and also how to engage your users throughout the purchasing process.<%2fp>				
